{"tid":679773,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"求驗客手記： 紅軍新門神　港女新男神","createTime":"2018-05-26T20:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T01:21:16.000Z","uid":53062,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2781a37d48fef0559397ca0267e0e94d01fa6e","tid":679773,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T20:54:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20160526/19627614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160526%2F19627614&d=uNcRTcFmtNPyZu%2FPobeCebIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8b2c734f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160526%2F19627614&h=a87c9206\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20160526/19627614</a><br />\n<br />\n利物浦喺周二落實由德甲緬恩斯收購門將卡利奧斯，相信唔少紅軍迷都讚好，終於有機會唔使再由後防炸彈米洛列特把關。不過有班非紅軍迷都一樣畀like，事關呢位22歲德國門將靚仔之餘，仲有型格紋身吸睛，未喺英超亮相先迷倒女粉絲。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未試過失誤累球隊失波</span></span><br />\n緬恩斯喺上季德甲長時間係爭逐歐聯參賽資格分子之一，卡利奧斯自然功不可沒。全季聯賽上陣34場失42球，聯賽失球率其實同米洛列特一樣；不過74.1%撲救成功就好過後者，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更重要係卡利奧斯全季未試過因為佢嘅失誤導致球隊失波</span></span>，而米生就有四次累紅軍失波，有個穩陣啲嘅門將，利物浦喺下季英超要捲土重來都有把握啲。原來佢都唔係第一次加盟英超球會，09年當佢16歲嗰陣，由史特加轉投曼城，但冇乜上位機會，兩年後就返咗德國加盟緬恩斯；亦因為效力過曼城，佢同𠵱家名義上仲係紅軍球員嘅巴洛迪利仲係朋友。 <br />\n<br />\nJB主動搭訕全因靚紋身<br />\n卡利奧斯好唔好波仲未知，但佢嘅加盟就令紅軍整體顏值提高唔少，六呎二吋身高加上俊朗外貌，仲有佢啲紋身圖案一樣養眼，心口有對比翼雙飛。亦因為紋身令佢喺上年結識咗加拿大歌星Justin Bieber，後者喺酒店泳池見佢啲紋身咁靚，就自動走埋去搭訕，之後交換電話做埋老友。除咗Bieber，相信卡利奧斯將會冧到唔少女球迷，唔少女粉絲已經喺社交網站度話要贒實佢。對於靚仔門神加盟利物浦，本身係紅軍球迷嘅鄧洢玲（阿旦）就相信紅軍嘅女球迷人數一定會上升喎。"},{"pid":"c3cec4c17f8f4700ee91eb53f4929ad0aca73865","tid":679773,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T20:59:13.000Z","msg":"如果踢中型班，鬼會完左聯賽仲有場決賽踢咩<br />\n<br />\n所以呢場唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我卡仍然冇累過球會輸波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ebf431dbe71cc0d296a04388a804f664a75f44","tid":679773,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:04:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20160621/00315_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20160621%2F00315_001.html&d=uNcRTcFmtNPyZu%2FPobeCebIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=4a19d5dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20160621/00315_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Kelena愛紅軍新戰衣愈嘈愈有Feel</strong><br />\n<br />\n常言道︰運動女生加10分，不過對無數男生而言，熱愛足球的女生，可能加分更多呢！身為利物浦天字第一號粉絲的「杰寧公主」Kelena就是最佳代表。雖然新一季的英超8月才開鑼，不過新球季的主場新球衣已經抵港，身為紅軍忠粉的Kelena，對這款新戰袍又有何評價？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新領位體貼女生</strong><br />\n紅色一向是利物浦的主場顏色，新球衣也不例外，Kelena直言：「最初對新球衣的印象未覺驚喜，不過細看之下，就會發現不少討人喜歡的細節，我最喜歡是衫腳印有THERE'S NO NOISE LIKE THE ANFIELD NOISE的口號，晏菲路球迷的打氣聲是全球聞名的，新球衣有了這句口號，令我充滿使命感，覺得所有紅軍球迷都要更加大大聲打氣。」另一方面，新球衣與上一屆同樣採用圓領剪裁，不過Kelena就大條道理貪新忘舊，她解釋說︰「為了避免對手拉扯，近期不少球衣的領位都採用較貼頸的設計，好似上一季紅軍球衣的領位便太窄，穿着有些不便；新球衣的領位多了鈕扣，穿着起來較容易、舒服得多，尤其是對女生而言，毋須再怕揩花面上的化妝，又不會整亂頭髮。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>球員版首度上架</strong><br />\n新球衣見證了New Balance與利物浦的第2季合作，另一驚喜之處，是新增了球員版行貨，功能性比球迷版高，例如兩腋多了以雷射切割而成的大型透氣位，衫身上多個接縫位改用無縫製法，穿着感受自然比球迷版更自在、更舒適。溫馨提示︰球員版的剪裁比球迷版窄身，想Carry得起的話，就要多多運動操Fit體形了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>公主論紅軍</strong><br />\n除了大讚新球衣，Kelena對新一季的利物浦也充滿期待，原因不外乎兩個男人，且看她有何高見︰<br />\n<br />\n<strong>帥哥新鋼門　刺激球迷人數<br />\n利物浦領隊高普 知人善任</strong><br />\n高普對球員的了解能力十分強，深知他們的能力、長處，亦會針對目前陣容的缺點而買入新球員。我期望利物浦在下一屆的英超進佔頭4位，至於英超冠軍，應該給予高普更多時間準備，我相信在他的領軍之下，我們會贏到英超冠軍的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20160621/photo/0621-00315-001b11.jpg?t=1527368573886\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20160621%2Fphoto%2F0621-00315-001b11.jpg%3Ft%3D1527368573886&h=1d27e4ea&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n卡利奧斯（Loris Karius）加盟，絕對是女球迷的一大福利，俊朗的外表，相信會幫紅軍吸引很多女球迷。而且他效力德國球隊緬恩斯時，已經<span style=\"color: red;\">表現出反應快、位置感強</span>，反觀原來的龍門米奴列，應付高空球的信心似乎不大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/050442_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F050442_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=d7bbcd5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fd179b7e8b7b49206cdbdb19b6f49663f82dd5e","tid":679773,"uid":4845,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:10:10.000Z","msg":"反應又真係幾快<br />\n電光火石間都比佢瞄到賓斯馬隻腳丟落去"},{"pid":"b29958cc265e97bbd8c09a12e203e72310404f7c","tid":679773,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:16:49.000Z","msg":"長期置頂"},{"pid":"5bd4a7238bb59975f13f1a1aa0a2e9bb3ea701c6","tid":679773,"uid":30040,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/051810_b0eb09f06962a7a85f8b3914651b2d94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F051810_b0eb09f06962a7a85f8b3914651b2d94.png&h=19d27e38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01340339bc34b90f89ee6b1ff7816de732918e12","tid":679773,"uid":123243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 猁狗"},{"pid":"4fba7abac555f301c42bd191e687750136be140b","tid":679773,"uid":175341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bd4a7238bb59975f13f1a1aa0a2e9bb3ea701c6","tid":679773,"uid":30040,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/051810_b0eb09f06962a7a85f8b3914651b2d94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F051810_b0eb09f06962a7a85f8b3914651b2d94.png&h=19d27e38&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:25:35.000Z","msg":"呢個好笑"},{"pid":"0fcffd373d87c09a34969607dccead9d73bf546b","tid":679773,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bd4a7238bb59975f13f1a1aa0a2e9bb3ea701c6","tid":679773,"uid":30040,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/051810_b0eb09f06962a7a85f8b3914651b2d94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F051810_b0eb09f06962a7a85f8b3914651b2d94.png&h=19d27e38&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b1a0fdce65e140a71db0707aa94a8286722011","tid":679773,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:57:05.000Z","msg":"講反應快得過米佬？女人真係唔撚識波"},{"pid":"ad2029a76b566e3611b76f506ec2d38f9b55d876","tid":679773,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T01:21:16.000Z","msg":"推"}]}